<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 15:11:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>克里姆林宫：普京和习近平拒绝美国的“干涉”，赞扬两国关系和贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-xi-reject-us-interference-praise-their-own-ties-trade-kremlin-2024-02-08/</link><description>克里姆林宫表示，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京和中国国家主席习近平周四通电话，两人都拒绝接受美国干涉其他国家事务的说法。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 13:18:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-xi-reject-us-interference-praise-their-own-ties-trade-kremlin-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>拉尔夫·劳伦 (Ralph Lauren) 乘着强劲的假日需求和中国市场反弹，公布了乐观的业绩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ralph-lauren-tops-quarterly-sales-estimate-strong-demand-2024-02-08/</link><description>受美国对其昂贵的羊绒毛衣、外套和鸡尾酒会礼服的强劲假期需求以及中国的强劲反弹推动，Ralph Lauren 的利润连续第 14 个季度超出预期，周四该公司股价上涨 11%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 13:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ralph-lauren-tops-quarterly-sales-estimate-strong-demand-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟的维斯塔格怀疑大型科技公司是否会完全遵守具有里程碑意义的欧盟规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eus-vestager-doubts-if-big-tech-will-fully-comply-with-landmark-eu-rules-2024-02-08/</link><description>欧盟反垄断主管玛格丽特·维斯塔格周四对大型科技公司是否会完全遵守欧盟旨在限制其权力并确保为较小竞争对手提供公平竞争环境的里程碑式规则表示怀疑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 12:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eus-vestager-doubts-if-big-tech-will-fully-comply-with-landmark-eu-rules-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>Tapestry 预计 2024 年利润将因中国需求而增加，利润率强劲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/coach-parent-tapestry-beats-quarterly-sales-estimates-2024-02-08/</link><description>Coach 母公司 Tapestry 周四上调了年度利润预期，押注其优质手袋和书包的全价销售以及主要市场中国需求复苏的早期迹象。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 11:53:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/coach-parent-tapestry-beats-quarterly-sales-estimates-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平与普京通话时敦促“密切战略协作”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-urges-close-strategic-coordination-call-with-putin-2024-02-08/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国国家主席习近平向俄罗斯总统普京表示，两国应密切战略协作，捍卫各自国家的主权、安全和发展利益。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 11:35:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-urges-close-strategic-coordination-call-with-putin-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯VTB银行首席执行官表示将扩大在中国的业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russias-vtb-bank-expand-presence-china-ceo-2024-02-08/</link><description>俄罗斯国有VTB银行首席执行官安德烈·科斯廷(Andrey Kostin)周四在与俄罗斯州长会面时表示，计划在不久的将来在北京和其他城市开设办事处，扩大在中国的业务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 11:22:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russias-vtb-bank-expand-presence-china-ceo-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>“消防员”吴在溃败后成为中国市场监管者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/firefighter-wu-becomes-chinas-market-regulator-after-rout-2024-02-08/</link><description>中国市场监管机构的新任负责人对内幕交易采取强硬态度，迅速扑救，与共产党领导人密切合作，并管理过一家证券交易所——这对于掌管中国陷入困境的股市的人来说是完美的形象。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 11:11:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/firefighter-wu-becomes-chinas-market-regulator-after-rout-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：标准普尔 500 指数创历史新高 5,000 点，中国泄气</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-08/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 11:04:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>Avolon首席执行官表示，波音公司“毫无疑问”在质量问题上取得了进展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-undoubtedly-making-progress-quality-issues-avolon-ceo-says-2024-02-08/</link><description>全球第二大飞机租赁公司、波音主要客户 Avolon 的负责人周四表示，波音在解决质量问题方面“毫无疑问”取得了重大进展。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:52:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-undoubtedly-making-progress-quality-issues-avolon-ceo-says-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>台湾感谢世界，解放军在新年贺词中展示模拟袭击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-thanks-world-pla-shows-simulated-attacks-new-years-messages-2024-02-08/</link><description>周四，蔡英文总统在农历新年致辞中感谢国际社会对台湾的支持。一天前，中国军方在模拟导弹袭击的图像中发布了一首敦促台湾“回家”的歌曲。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:04:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-thanks-world-pla-shows-simulated-attacks-new-years-messages-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>美国称领先的人工智能公司加入安全联盟以应对风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-says-leading-ai-companies-join-safety-consortium-address-risks-2024-02-08/</link><description>拜登政府周四表示，200 多家实体加入了一个新的美国财团，以支持生成式人工智能的安全开发和部署，其中包括领先的人工智能公司。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:03:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-says-leading-ai-companies-join-safety-consortium-address-risks-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>安赛乐米塔尔预计今年除中国以外的钢铁需求将增长3-4%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/arcelormittal-expects-3-4-steel-demand-growth-ex-china-this-year-2024-02-08/</link><description>全球第二大钢铁制造商安赛乐米塔尔周四表示，看到行业背景正在改善的初步迹象，预计今年中国以外的全球钢铁需求将增长 3-4%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 09:42:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/arcelormittal-expects-3-4-steel-demand-growth-ex-china-this-year-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>一年过去了，一位中国明星交易撮合者的缺席给他的银行蒙上了一层阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/one-year-star-chinese-dealmakers-absence-casts-pall-over-his-bank-2024-02-08/</link><description>包凡被中国当局带走，此后同事就再也没有见过他。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 09:31:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/one-year-star-chinese-dealmakers-absence-casts-pall-over-his-bank-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>研究人员称，在华朝鲜工人中出现罕见的骚乱迹象</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/signs-rare-unrest-among-north-korean-workers-china-researchers-say-2024-02-08/</link><description>韩国情报机构表示，朝鲜人在海外工作的恶劣条件导致了“事件和事故”，而研究人员报告称，中国一家与朝鲜军方有联系的贸易公司的工人在中国发生了罕见的抗议和骚乱。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 07:50:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/signs-rare-unrest-among-north-korean-workers-china-researchers-say-2024-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>美元坚挺、中国经济困境削弱信心，亚洲外汇空头坚守阵地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/asian-fx-bears-hold-ground-robust-dollar-china-woes-dent-confidence-2024-02-08/</link><description>路透周四的一项调查显示，对大多数亚洲货币的空头押注略有缓解，但仍坚定地处于看跌区域，原因是美国提前降息的希望减弱，使美元保持强劲，而区域强国中国的市场波动削弱了投资者信心。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 07:19:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/asian-fx-bears-hold-ground-robust-dollar-china-woes-dent-confidence-2024-02-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>